## `app.css` — Global Mobile Utilities

These classes/rules are in `ui/static/css/app.css` and apply to all dashboard pages:

| Rule | Effect at mobile |
|---|---|
| `.page-container` | `margin: 1rem auto` at 768px |
| `.card-body` / `.card-header` | Reduced padding at 768px and 480px |
| `.modal-dialog` | `margin: 0.5rem` at 768px, `margin: 0.25rem` at 480px |
| `.toast-container` | Moves to **bottom** of screen (`bottom: 16px; left/right: 8px`) |
| `.alert-container` | Same — moves to bottom, full-width |
| `.file-upload-area` | Reduced padding at 768px |

---

## Per-Page Responsive Patterns

Every dashboard template has an inline `<style>` block with `@media (max-width: 768px)`. The standard pattern for containers:

```css
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .my-container {
        margin: 1rem auto;
        padding: 0 0.5rem;
    }
    .my-header {
        padding: 1.25rem;   /* down from 2rem */
    }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
    .my-container { /* further reductions for very small phones */ }
}
```

### Grids — Collapsing on Mobile

| Desktop | Mobile (`≤768px`) |
|---|---|
| `repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr))` | Becomes 1-col via `grid-template-columns: 1fr` |
| `repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr))` | Stays 2-col (`1fr 1fr`) |
| `.stats-cards` (4 cols) | Becomes `1fr 1fr` (2-col) |
| `.resume-score-cards` (2 cols) | Becomes `1fr` |
| `.iv-logistics-grid` | Becomes `1fr` |
| `.talking-points-grid` | Becomes `1fr` |
| `.jd-glance-grid` | Becomes `repeat(2, 1fr)` |
| `.resume-skills-cols` | Becomes `1fr` |
| `.applications-list` (dashboard) | Single-col cards; filter bar scrolls horizontally |

